A simple Todo App built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Add, manage, and track your tasks easily!

🔗 Live Demo: https://todo-app-example.vercel.app (Example link, replace with yours)

✨ Features
✔ Add tasks – Type and press Enter or click the "Add" button.
✔ Task list – View all your tasks in a clean list.
✔ Responsive design – Works on desktop and mobile.
✔ No backend needed – Pure frontend (tasks are saved in browser memory).

